-- Hong Kong to Offer Immigrants Insurance-Residency Plan, Newspaper Reports
-- Stanley James
-- 2010-06-17T22:59:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/hong-kong-to-offer-immigrants-insurance-residency-plan-newspaper-reports.html

          
          
             Hong Kong plans to offer migrants
residency if they spend HK$6.5 million on investment-linked
insurance policies, the South China Morning Post said, citing
people familiar with the policy. The government may announce the
new policy as early as next week, according to the report.  
          
          


  


        